content: Fuel Filter Hoses May Disconnect and Leak Fuel

Jayco, Inc. (Jayco) is recalling certain 2024-2025 Entegra Anthem, Aspire, and 2025 Reatta XL motorhomes, equipped with Cummins L9 diesel engines.  The remote fuel filter hose may separate from the fitting, causing a fuel leak and an engine stall.A fuel leak in the presence of an ignition source increases the risk of a fire.  An engine stall increases the risk of a crash.

Number of Units Affected: 34.0"
